  "body": "This should only be used in very rare cases e.g. if you are not 100% sure if something is a bug or asking a question that leads to improving the documentation. For general questions please use [discord](https://discord.gg/nthXNEv) or the Ethereum stack exchange at https://ethereum.stackexchange.com.\r\n\r\nThis machine has been synced successfully with a previous version of geth, but after rebooting and upgrading for some special reasons, the status can no longer be synced successfully\r\n\r\nThis is the ssd disk speed test of the server\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/13202561/201563341-ac2ec875-c06c-4c11-9d81-ad44a39bbd5e.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nI have used the latest geth program as well as the latest beacon nodes (sigp/lighthouse)\r\n\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/13202561/201564087-e7e819c6-d7ba-45ea-b9cb-8a168dc6d4ce.png)\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/13202561/201591906-68f3a8ff-8237-4a60-b258-5363142e7e2e.png)\r\n\r\n\r\nMy internet bandwidth can reach a speed of 50MB/s during the download block phase, and I don't think the internet speed is too slow\r\n\r\n\r\n",
